      "value": "<p>You’re an expert at picking a pocket and running.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: When attempting a Sleight of Hand check to pick a pocket, you can immediately attempt a Stealth check to hide with a –5 penalty. You must have appropriate cover or concealment. Your target’s opposed Perception check to notice the pick-pocket attempt is against your Stealth check result, as opposed to your Sleight of Hand result.</p>"
